text: Honest Moyo (born 29 October 1991) is a Zimbabwe Bulawayoan footballer who plays as a defender for TS Sporting and the Zimbabwean national football team. ==Career== In March 2019, Moyo joined TS Sporting in South Africa.Ex-Bosso skipper finds new home at TS Sporting, nehandaradio.com, 4 March 2019 ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Highlanders F.C. players Category:TS Sporting F.C. players Category:Zimbabwe Premier Soccer League players Category:Zimbabwean footballers Category:Zimbabwe international footballers Category:Association football defenders
